{"tid":1534931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《手足情》4／9 至7／9係休息期","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:04:30.000Z","uid":8948,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"00ef25a021b6d2cbd4122c36007f0e3b05c65757","tid":1534931,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"八月尾九月頭接連都有唔同活動＋集會<br />\n不論係前線，後勤，文宣，和理非都過左好多晚痛心既無眠夜，<br />\n無數既負面資訊排山倒海咁湧入腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候抖一抖，回一回氣<br />\n保持抗爭力量，休息係好重要既一環<br />\n我建議黎緊每個weekend 都只需要keep住一次大型活動<br />\n其餘飯後活動就因各區而異，但大前提係不被捕，保持抗爭人數<br />\n<br />\n首先用10分鐘照顧一下自己心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/%E7%94%A8-10-%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/444597819473358/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F%25E7%2594%25A8-10-%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E7%2585%25A7%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%2F444597819473358%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=cd90c7dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/%E7%94%A8-10-%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/444597819473358/</a><br />\n<br />\n嘗試擺低所有新聞，做一啲自己好耐冇做既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靜靜地飲杯咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇返甩左好耐既劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，去戲院睇返套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同朋友食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，見下女男朋友（如果有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），睇下女優有冇新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等等<br />\n<br />\n然後每晚十點鐘就將所有憤怒化為行動，十點鐘對窗大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qrpi8cy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrpi8cy.jpg&h=97148ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>休息不是遺忘，是為了一起走下去。<br />\n<br />\n香港人！加油！贏就一齊贏，輸就一齊輸，一個都不能少！<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=44deafc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n同意請正評推post"},{"pid":"5545d4d7ec62ae1bd1a2069235dfa9af2811dfdb","tid":1534931,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"575dc25143e118e8a3742784930527f250c294cb","tid":1534931,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"90a0a13661cf37caba33b76f0bee590eedf286d7","tid":1534931,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"好痛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2c74c926ca638c64ba40a7880cab5dd20a67f0","tid":1534931,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a44c5631f780df7c9854d1963f35d8914a2a44b3","tid":1534931,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a0a13661cf37caba33b76f0bee590eedf286d7","tid":1534931,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"好痛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"喊下，係可以的"},{"pid":"65a9c7488f3681c9a0706a437aee9b1dc0e5fc0f","tid":1534931,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc965cdefe2101070730db7b9049d2a8118f1630","tid":1534931,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e91a0e3ac4d9c1397e67c9e6430acaa7601157d","tid":1534931,"uid":314556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"707b1211f8f3b22772c3223100ae740672b74ace","tid":1534931,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d84a42cc6a7f4cd236ef24423109f88a95c3038","tid":1534931,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09